OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry this
OL,6,Fevening with some late sunshine. Then
OL,7,Fthe rest of the night will be dry with
OL,8,Fclear periods but the east may become
OL,9,Fcloudy.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FDry with plenty of sunshine
OL,12,Fbut eastern Aberdeenshire may be
OL,13,Frather cool and cloudy. Warm inland,
OL,14,Flocally very warm across Moray.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDry on
OL,17,FFriday with bright spells, western
OL,18,FAberdeenshire will be rather cloudy.
OL,19,FOutbreaks of rain spreading east on
OL,20,FSaturday. A few showers possible on
OL,21,FSunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
